  <entry>
    <title>數值補零-(Padding Left)</title>
    <url>/2020/11/22/paddingLeft/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>偶爾我們會遇上固定顯示幾位數的狀況，這裡一個簡易的方法來提供補零的方式，如果有任何更好的方法歡迎在下面提供。</p>
<h2 id="Code"><a href="#Code" class="headerlink" title="Code"></a>Code</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">function</span> paddingLeft(str,strLenght)&#123;  </span><br><span class="line">  var thisStr=String(str),//如果沒有強行別,在放在計算裡面會轉成INT,造成undefined</span><br><span class="line">      thisStrlenght=parseInt(strLenght);//所以我數字也順便加上型別了 QQ      </span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">if</span>(thisStr.length &gt;= thisStrlenght)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">return</span> str;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;<span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;       </span><br><span class="line">        var makeupNum= thisStrlenght - thisStr.length,</span><br><span class="line">            makeZero=<span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            //原本可以利用callback 重複補0,但我希望函式只要用一次就可以補完所有的0</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">for</span>(var i=0;i&lt;makeupNum;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                makeZero= makeZero+<span class="string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;     </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">return</span> makeZero+thisStr;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;	</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">//使用的方式</span><br><span class="line">var test_text=paddingLeft(1,20);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>More info: [codePen]](<a href="https://codepen.io/CKman/pen/vYELbeq">https://codepen.io/CKman/pen/vYELbeq</a>)</p>
]]></content>
